Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.77,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Our most powerful and final weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.22,0:00:10.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The final battle will be at \Nthe Flames of Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:12.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,In order for you to have
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.54,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,the time to truly decide whether \Nthis world is worth saving or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:19.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,we need the world to keep existing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.99,Bullet_Main,jerk,0000,0000,0000,,This will mean the end of Satomi Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:05.64,Bullet_Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(460,515)}#13 The Ones Who Aspired to Be Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:12.40,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,The Gastrea are projected \Nto arrive in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:14.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't the batteries come yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.23,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any Gastrea in my field of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,What useful eyesight she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.24,Bullet_Main,kohina,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, Owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:27.00,Bullet_Main,sumi,0000,0000,0000,,But not all of the civil officers \Nhave powers like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.22,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,There's no contact from the JASDF, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:32.26,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,If we haven't received them by now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.17,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,we should assume we \Nwon't receive them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:39.76,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,The Gastrea army have \Ncome through the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.97,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,They are heading straight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.72,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, at this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.04,0:02:47.38,Bullet_Main,tama,0000,0000,0000,,Either the enemy comes \Nat us and we perish...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.23,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,...or we go after the enemy and perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.30,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,They will arrive in about five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All units, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.42,0:02:59.24,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.39,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.26,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What... are those lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:14.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the Genan Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:21.71,Bullet_Italics,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san, it is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.09,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Seitenshi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.56,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So you did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.02,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.63,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,each one of these lights is filled
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.63,0:03:38.73,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,with the hopes of the \Ncitizens of the Tokyo Area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:42.71,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,as well as their prayers, \Nand their will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.70,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,I am leaving the future of the \NTokyo Area in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.87,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Go...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:54.50,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,With the courage to never give up, \Nno matter what the battle, and to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:56.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:00.01,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.47,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I believe people have two faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:06.13,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Light and dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:08.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:14.14,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,If you can see the prayers and hope \Nfilling each one of these lights...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:16.43,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.77,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.47,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,The Gastrea are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.91,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And Aldebaran is at the rear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:31.66,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We will now commence operation \N"Rapier's Thrust!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:55.98,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All right. We're moving on to stage two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.23,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All units, advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.48,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.86,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,I will assist with the assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.95,Bullet_Italics,miori,0000,0000,0000,,A giant Gastrea is heading \Nstraight toward us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.51,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Satomi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:33.64,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.64,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.71,Bullet_Main,Shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Style Martial Arts:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.82,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Homura Kasen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.31,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,So this is death...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:04.78,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,So this is war...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:07.47,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:16.23,Bullet_Main,kage,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be wasting \Ntime here, Leader Satomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:18.07,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:19.69,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:25.90,Bullet_Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Aldebaran is now only 100 meters away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:27.40,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.87,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Enju!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We will now eliminate the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.10,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This is the—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.03,0:07:00.77,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.38,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,The EP bomb has been set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:28.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go off in one minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.31,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,All units, fall back as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.66,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:43.52,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Five, four, three, two, one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.14,0:07:52.20,Bullet_Main,miori,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.96,0:07:55.62,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Miori... Did it fail to go off?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:03.88,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Ren...taro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.39,Bullet_Italics,miori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Satomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.36,0:08:11.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.25,0:08:14.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:15.91,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:19.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:20.52,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.99,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I always...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:27.61,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to be a person worthy of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:32.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,For the year since I met you, I was truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:35.61,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly thankful
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,that I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:43.79,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Don't g—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:59.39,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,If I can apply enough direct force, \Nthe EP bomb should go off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.64,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.14,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,But only
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.57,Bullet_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,at point blank range!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:12.76,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Ren...taro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.00,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Varanium-corroding fluid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:29.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:36.43,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:40.93,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more... and Aldebaran will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.19,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.19,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi, looks like they got you good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:09:59.20,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Shoma-nii...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.69,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.20,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure I've figured \Nout what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:04.93,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:11.24,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,We have to... send an shock \Nwave deep into its body...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:18.05,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,My attack has the ability to destroy \Nopponents from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.44,0:10:20.72,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No, Shoma-nii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:25.95,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No! You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:28.44,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,My attack is considered heresy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.13,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,I have to seal this attack \Ndeep within the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.93,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Aldebaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.97,0:10:39.13,Bullet_Main,shoma,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.45,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Live on for my sake, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:43.47,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Shoma-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.73,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.26,0:11:32.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:42.55,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Shoma-nii... along with Aldebaran...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.01,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I know... Tina saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:48.27,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,What about the remaining Gastrea?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:52.81,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,After Aldebaran exploded, \Ntheir movements became strange
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:56.15,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,and they started to scatter, \Nso they were easy to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them escaped outside \Nof the Monoliths, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.96,0:12:04.04,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.25,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.59,0:12:07.92,Bullet_Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.58,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... all that's left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.49,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,This is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:42.27,Bullet_Italics,ren,0000,0000,0000,,With the destruction of the \NStage Four Gastrea, Aldebaran,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.27,Bullet_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,humanity won The Third Kanto Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.63,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,It has been two days since the \Nvictory of the Kanto Battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.45,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,and it appears that the construction \Nof the new Monolith 32
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.28,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,is progressing as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.76,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,The height has already surpassed 300 meters,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:06.17,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,and it is presumed to be greatly \Naffecting Gastrea in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.81,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,We have arrived, Kazumitsu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:22.33,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Kazumitsu-oniisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.66,0:13:23.81,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.81,0:13:25.91,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Should I call you the Vice Minister
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.03,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,of Land, Infrastructure, \NTransport, and Tourism?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.88,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.62,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,And I see you have a child, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.99,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the promised item?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:47.93,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I thought I got rid of all these...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:51.78,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I had always thought it was strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:56.19,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Aldebaran stick itself to the Monolith?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,The one who was placing orders for materials
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:03.64,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,for Monolith 32 towards the \Nend of the Gastrea War...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.95,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.81,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can approve of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.71,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,mixing other ingredients with the Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:14.71,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,so the Monolith could be \Nmade cheaply and you could
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.29,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,pocket the rest of the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.96,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Logically, that purity should have been fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:22.21,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't work on Aldebaran.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.89,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,And with the money you appropriated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.57,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,you were able to achieve \Nyour current status.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:32.83,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,The one who pulled the trigger \Non the Third Kanto Battle is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.79,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the pieces of \Nhuman trash that should have
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.14,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,died in the battle with the Gastrea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.15,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,A true villain doesn't perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.64,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I can throw money around,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:47.03,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and while "death" is picking that up, I can flee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.33,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Both parties, bring forth a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.83,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,I, Shiina Kazumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.90,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,am here to witness this duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.86,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that, even if either \Nparticipant in this duel is killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:06.55,Bullet_Main,kazumi,0000,0000,0000,,I will not go to the police or any \Nother administration of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:10.84,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two really have to go \Nthrough with this duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:15.97,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro, I must forever silence this \Nwench's mouth right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:19.54,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, I've been waiting ten years for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.24,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally tracked down one \Nof the people responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,for my mother and father's deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.90,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,My battle with him is my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:33.28,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:37.79,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts Divine Spear \Npractitioner, Tendo Kazumitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:42.00,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword Drawing \Npractitioner, Tendo Kisara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:08.81,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,What is that style?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:12.36,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword Drawing, \NRyukosogeki stance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.22,0:16:15.39,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,It is the style that I created to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.49,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,destroy every member of the Tendo family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:19.08,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Enough nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.83,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Amako Genmeika!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:39.77,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Tendo Martial Arts Sword \NDrawing Zero Style, Number 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:41.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Agiosotoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.65,0:16:45.49,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,That is the name of the move \NI used to strike you, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:49.23,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zero Style?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:51.95,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,It is one strike, yet two.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.16,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,The second strike is faster \Nthan the speed of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:17:01.00,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't see the second strike \Nthat severed your left leg, Onii-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:05.00,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Onii-sama, talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.91,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,About the attack ten years ago \Nin which my parents were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.73,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that stray Gastrea appearing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.63,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,in the heart of the Tokyo Area is plausible?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:18.01,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:23.61,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There were a total of five \Nwho were involved in the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:28.02,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Myself, three of my brothers, \Nand Tendo Kikunojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.77,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:36.45,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Father was going to expose the \Ndarkness of the Tendo clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.73,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.59,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Everything like what just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.97,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,For the Tendo clan to obtain its current status,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.97,0:17:46.02,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,many similar incidents have happened over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:50.05,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Father suddenly decided \Nhe was going to go public with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.63,0:17:54.09,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,So we planned to eliminate him, \Nalong with the rest of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:56.98,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:17:59.22,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you going to spare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:04.10,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, Enju-chan, Tina-chan, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.92,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.72,Bullet_Main,kazu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:19.36,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, he's annoying, \Nso could you shut the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.32,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:24.07,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Kisara-san, is this really...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.07,0:18:25.83,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,It is one strike, yet two.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:27.72,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.21,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,the second strike didn't just take his leg...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:32.71,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.27,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.27,Bullet_Main,tina,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:55.78,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.85,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:06.91,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I finally killed one of the people \Nresponsible for my parents' deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.71,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.88,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:18.06,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy, Satomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.68,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,This is our revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:23.35,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It was {\i1}your{\i0} execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:26.33,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you kill Kazumitsu-niisan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:29.80,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,You knew before you did it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.94,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Where is there justice in that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.14,0:19:39.01,Bullet_Main,ksia,0000,0000,0000,,Satomi-kun, I've realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:42.52,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't able to slay Tendo Kikunojo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.52,0:19:46.29,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,who was behind the Kagetane \Nincident, or Saitake Sogen,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.09,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,who was behind the sniping incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.62,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to slay Tendo Kazumitsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.63,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.28,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Because I am "evil."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.32,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,Your fists of justice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.80,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,can never touch evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.37,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,It is not justice that can oppose evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.40,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,It is an absolute evil that \Noverpowers evil itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.86,0:20:18.53,Bullet_Main,kisa,0000,0000,0000,,I have that power... I just confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.65,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Tina... Enju...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:32.85,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I might end up as Kisara-san's enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.31,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we have overcome \Nthis national crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:42.99,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,we have been given another \Nchance at harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:46.59,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that establishing \Nthe New Gastrea Law
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:51.39,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,will let many of the souls who \Ndied in this battle finally rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:57.55,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, we are having girls, \Nwho are all very young,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.36,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,bear too heavy a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.57,0:21:05.23,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,At this time, there may not \Nbe any other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:08.42,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,However, in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:11.53,Bullet_Main,seiteen,0000,0000,0000,,there may come a day when \Ntheir burden can be lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:16.26,Bullet_Main,seiten,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is us who will make that day a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:25.49,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Ceremony of conferment of decoration?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:28.68,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. At the Sacred Palace \Nwhere Seitenshi-sama lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.34,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they're going to congratulate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:34.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Is this attire appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.51,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.19,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.43,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.28,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Here. This is for you, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:46.70,Bullet_Main,rentaro,0000,0000,0000,,An oath?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.09,0:21:50.75,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,"One: You will not face an enemy alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.75,0:21:53.41,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Two: We will do everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:57.46,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Three: Don't knock me \Nunconscious without warning"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:21:58.38,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:00.39,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,"Four"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:08.72,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,A fatal accident has occurred \Nat the Third District Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:10.29,Bullet_Announcer,announcer,0000,0000,0000,,We request your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:14.52,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're going to be late...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.63,0:22:17.35,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.35,0:22:22.98,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it was painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:28.36,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Was there nothing that we could have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.83,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:44.00,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter, Rentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:46.76,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I'm becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:48.98,Bullet_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,unaffected by the deaths of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.90,0:22:53.22,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Enju... Please stay by my side, always...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.02,Bullet_Main,ren,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let me go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:04.37,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Rentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:10.34,Bullet_Main,enju,0000,0000,0000,,You and I will always be \Ntogether, forever and ever.
